      <title>欧洲央行行长莱恩表示明年工资增长将大幅放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ecb-s-lane-says-wage-growth-set-to-ease-significantly-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，欧元区工人的工资增长——通胀的主要驱动因素——将在 2025 年和 2026 年大幅放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ecb-s-lane-says-wage-growth-set-to-ease-significantly-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 11:16:03 GMT</pubDate>
